snippet.title: From the Shadows - Trailer
snippet.description:
From the Shadows is a cooperative puzzle platformer game. Explore a haunted castle filled with puzzles, traps and secrets. Will you find your way out?
Download the game for free at https://gamagora.itch.io/from-the-shadows
Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/teamspookyggs
